  "key_insight": "The largest WIP band at May 16, 2026 is 'Awaiting Review' with 61 items in flight. The thicker that band is on the chart, the more work is queued or in-progress at that stage; the steeper the line bordering it, the faster items are arriving into the stage.",
  "next_actions": [
    "Investigate why items accumulate in 'Awaiting Review'. Either items are arriving faster than this stage can process, or they're waiting on a downstream resource (reviewers, environments, decisions).",
